items.name: Animagine XL
items.description:
ANIMAGINE XL

Huggingface link: https://huggingface.co/Linaqruf/animagine-xl
Gradio Demo : https://huggingface.co/spaces/Linaqruf/Animagine-XL

Training model is expensive, please consider to support us at : https://ko-fi.com/linaqruf

Overview

Animagine XL is a high-resolution, latent text-to-image diffusion model. The model has been fine-tuned using a learning rate of 4e-7 over 27000 global steps with a batch size of 16 on a curated dataset of superior-quality anime-style images. This model is derived from Stable Diffusion XL 1.0.

  • Use it with the Stable Diffusion Webui

  • Use it with 🧨 diffusers

  • Use it with the ComfyUI (recommended)

Like other anime-style Stable Diffusion models, it also supports Danbooru tags to generate images.

e.g. face focus, cute, masterpiece, best quality, 1girl, green hair, sweater, looking at viewer, upper body, beanie, outdoors, night, turtleneck

How to Use:

  • It's recommended to setup ComfyUI before downloading the model.

  • We provided the workflow here https://huggingface.co/Linaqruf/animagine-xl/resolve/main/animagine_xl_workflow.json

  • You need to use Danbooru-style tag as prompt instead of natural language, otherwise you will get realistic result instead of anime

  • You can use any generic negative prompt or use the following suggested negative prompt to guide the model towards high aesthetic generationse:

lowres, bad anatomy, bad hands, text, error, missing fingers, extra digit, fewer digits, cropped, worst quality, low quality, normal quality, jpeg artifacts, signature, watermark, username, blurry

  • And, the following should also be prepended to prompts to get high aesthetic results:

masterpiece, best quality

  • Use this cheat sheet to find the best resolution:

768 x 1344: Vertical (9:16)
915 x 1144: Portrait (4:5)
1024 x 1024: Square (1:1)
1182 x 886: Photo (4:3)
1254 x 836: Landscape (3:2)
1365 x 768: Widescreen (16:9)
1564 x 670: Cinematic (21:9)

items.name: Gamora (Guardians of the Galaxy) (LoRA SDXL 1.0)
items.description:
This LoRA has been trained after carefully selecting 102 images, most of them from Guardian of the Galaxy vol. 1 and 2. All photos have been enhanced to make the most of them.

When downloading model and testing it, try to copy any of the prompts I have used, and make some variations in order to get other images you prefer. Have fun!

There is a great range of improvement in base model, especially regarding weird limbs or hands (yes, it's still there!! :( ) Anyway I'm satisfied with this model, waiting for future improved photorealistic checkpoints based on SDXL base 1.0.

LoRA weights should be between 0.8 and 1.3 in my experience (but you're free to test)

For portraits you can use 896 x 1152, 768 x 1344, 832 x 1216, 640 x 1536 or even 768x1024 resolutions.

I don't ask for anything but any respectful constructive review (after having tested the model) would be highly appreciated or at least press Like if you're happy with results after trying it out! Thanks in advance and enjoy it!

Notice: This free work is intended for art and illustration purposes of emergent technology and not intended nor' trained for making illicit images, as the author I've taken care to not use any private data in the training process or designed it for such purposes. By downloading this model you are agreeing with the aforementioned intent and that you will not use my work to create / share images of a potentially immoral and / or illegal nature.

items.name: Scaled Humanoid / Dragon Girls
items.description: Creates humanoids with scale patterns on their body. Lots of dragon girls in the dataset so it is likely to produce horns, tails, and wings or shapes that look those. Putting (tail, wings:1.2) usually clears those up but you may need to clean up the image. Most of the dataset was also front facing, so I suggest playing with weight when doing that angle. Otherwise, using 0.8-1.0 is advised. Adding high-strength skin colors such as (red skin:1.2) can generate more scales. Adding various prompts like claws or animal feet can also create more emphasis on hands or feet.

items.name: 【再世】next life-陈百强
items.description:
这是群星再世第六十三期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

中国香港歌手、原创音乐人。 陈百强是香港乐坛全盛时期代表性人物之一，也是中国首位登上奥运会舞台的明星。他擅长音乐创作，获得过众多音乐奖项。他也是香港流行乐坛史上第一位偶像歌手。代表作《偏偏喜欢你》《一生何求》《等》《涟漪》等。在音乐修为而言，陈百强真可称得上是一位多面手。他懂得作曲，写的词也不差。除了歌唱的好，也弹得一手好琴。在香港乐坛像陈百强这样“周身刀”的歌手其实十分难得。

“我俩很相似，从不懂和陌生人打交道，看似很会交际应酬，其实傻乎乎，但外人总说我们对人冷淡，高不可攀。陈百强虽然是个大孩子，但是他很明白事理，是个性情中人，而我也是。”

也许我会永远戴着那对儿珍珠耳环。

1993年，陈百强昏迷住院一年半后，因医治无效去世，年仅35岁。

CLIP Skip: 2

0. Drafting (512 x 512 res to find your desired sketch)
1. Hires fix (txt2img: 768 x 768, 768 x 512, 512 x 768, or above res)
2. inpaint (img2img: refine some unwanted effect, [Euler a] with 50+ step)
3. Upscaling (img2img: res*2 with [ControlNet Tile] & Ultimate SD upscale)

I always skip Step 0, 2 :P

modelVersions.name: Beta_0.4.1.1-BakedVAE
modelVersions.description:
DynaVision XL Beta 0.4.1.1 Public Release 08/25/23

This had some major reworking under the hood, as I'm trying to replace some of the earlier LORA builders that have issues with watermarks and signatures. it's an ongoing process and right now they're still a known issue, but they'll be something I'll be actively working on to fix moving forward. The reworking has changed the color balance of the output somewhat to something a bit more neutral - in a way this is better for doing proper post color work, and it looks just fine on it's own, but when compared directly in an x/y, the shift in color balance is subtle, but it's there. I've found the best way to bring the color back now is to use a bit higher CFG, with 7.5 being the sweet spot I've found.

Look for coherence improvements, a bit more detailed backgrounds and skin (though not too much, I want to keep that realistic stylized cartoon feel), less issues with splotchy irises and less racial bias. This also had an update merge with NightVision XL 0.6.8.1

LORAs Added

  • xl_real_beta

  • Grit-SDXL

  • MovieStillMasteryV03

  • greengirl (CokCok1.0)

Known Issues

  • hands

  • signatures and watermarks

  • Nipples are acting up again, I've noticed on occasion they're showing up on clothes again, and occasionally show up malformed. It seems it's trying to add piercings to nipples sometimes, and I've had luck with adding "nipple piercing" to my negatives if you find them giving you grief.

modelVersions.name: Beta_0.3.7.1.BakedVAE

BETA 0.3.7.1 CHANGELOG 08/12/23

NSFW Update! DynaVisionXL should be much easier to produce spicier and sexier images. Female anatomy should represent better in general. Male anatomy is still laughable, that's on the known issue list. Also worked on eyes a bit on this update as well, you should notice they look better overall with less goofy shaped irises and pupils (though not completely banished). With this release I'm switching to beta, and will slow down a bit with development.

Changes

  • greatly improved NSFW output capabilities

  • hands have seen a minor improvement, fingernails seem to be represented much better now

  • eyes should be better at distance and should see less odd iris/pupil shapes.

  • ADDED LORAS

    • DetailedEyes_XL_V2

    • finenude_v0_2a

Known Issues

- Hands are still hit or miss, though they're starting to become more hit than miss thankfully.

- Eyes at a distance are mostly fixed now, but can still sometimes look wonky.

- I noticed on some of the test images that nipples may be a bit overrepresented and may be a side effect of the NSFW enhancements. will need to watch and test.
